teams.description:
ChangeInFocus.org is the largest online buzz marketing campaign to promote Micro-Lending as THE means to alleviate third world poverty!

Our movement is based on the following three principles:
1. Every person has the ability to pull themselves out of poverty if given the correct tools;
2. Fostering personal connections and international relationships inspires people to help their worldly “neighbors” and;
3. Harnessing the social networking and communication power of the internet is the fastest and most effective means to fight poverty.
